OL,3,CCould patients soon have to pay for
OL,4,Chospital stays in Guernsey?
OL,6,FPatients in Guernsey could soon have
OL,7,Fto pay for some hospital stays, x-rays
OL,8,Fand consultants as the island's Health
OL,9,FCommittee President says he is
OL,10,Fconsidering ending free secondary
OL,11,Fhealthcare.
OL,13,FThe news comes after health
OL,14,Fprofessionals say that without change,
OL,15,Fthe service will collapse in 20 years.
