OL,3,CCould patients soon have to pay for
OL,4,Chospital stays in Guernsey?
OL,6,FGuernsey's Chief Minister, Deputy
OL,7,FLindsay De Sausmarez, explains: "We've
OL,8,Fgot a trend of a rising demand for
OL,9,Fhealth and social care, and if we are
OL,10,Fto do nothing about that, it is going
OL,11,Fto become unsustainable.
OL,13,F"So the first part of that process is
OL,14,Fto decide what services we need to
OL,15,Fprovide for the community and then
OL,16,Fagree how it can be found in a
OL,17,Fsustainable way."
