OL,3,CCould patients soon have to pay for
OL,4,Chospital stays in Guernsey?
OL,6,FCurrently, patients only pay for
OL,7,Fprimary healthcare such as GP visits,
OL,8,Fprescriptions, A&E treatment and
OL,9,Fambulances.
OL,11,FHowever, secondary or specialist care
OL,12,Fsuch as consultant fees, X-rays, MRIs
OL,13,Fand hospital stays are covered by
OL,14,FSocial Security contributions.
OL,16,FDeputy George Oswald, President of
OL,17,FGuernsey's Health and Social Care
OL,18,FCommittee, says the current system
OL,19,Fneeds updating.
