OL,6,FHe explains: "We cannot hide our heads
OL,7,Fin the sand, we are faced with an
OL,8,Fissue whereby if we don't address it,
OL,9,Fit will lead to significant issues in
OL,10,Fthe future.
OL,12,F"An issue which has been discussed in
OL,13,Fmany health care models is board and
OL,14,Flodging fees. I'm emphasising that if
OL,15,Fwe are to look at that, to look at
OL,16,Fmost certainly elective procedures,
OL,17,Fnot emergency procedures, where people
OL,18,Fhave no control over this.
