OL,6,F"I remember the old days of when
OL,7,Fpeople were significantly financially
OL,8,Fembarrassed by unexpected medical
OL,9,Fcosts, and I would make it absolutely
OL,10,Fclear that there is no way we are
OL,11,Fgoing to return to that situation."
OL,13,FResidents told ITV News that such
OL,14,Fcosts for hospital treatment would
OL,15,Fcause them financial issues.
OL,17,FOne islander says: "I'm going to be 78
OL,18,Fand I couldn't afford that at all."
