OL,6,FAnother adds: "I am struggling enough
OL,7,Ffor stuff because I'm in and out of
OL,8,Fdoctors all the time, so if I am
OL,9,Fhaving to pay for the hospital as
OL,10,Fwell, it's just so much stress."
OL,12,FA third explains: "I wouldn't have any
OL,13,Fmoney left if I had to pay for the
OL,14,Fhospital. I admire what the hospital
OL,15,Fdoes, they save lives, but no."
