OL,7,Freform by the end of the term to
OL,8,Fimprove financial stability and end
OL,9,Funcertainty over the island's tax
OL,10,Fstrategy, balancing the budget while
OL,11,Fsupporting infrastructure investment
OL,12,Fand rebuilding cash reserves.
