OL,6,FAsk the States to bring in changes to
OL,7,Fhealth and social care "to deliver a
OL,8,Fsystem suitable in scale and size for
OL,9,Fthe island", and agree on a long-term
OL,10,Fcare model.
OL,12,FBring in a strategy that defines the
OL,13,Ffollowing: States' goals for a "family-
OL,14,Ffriendly community", access to early
OL,15,Fyears health services, funding and
OL,16,Fquality of childcare and early
OL,17,Feducation, manages gaps and risks in
OL,18,Fservices for vulnerable children,
OL,19,Fprovides opportunities for Guernsey
OL,20,Ffamilies, and integrates services with
OL,21,Fmodern, fit-for-purpose legislation.
